title: Shauna Howe // 90
description:
In 1992, an 11-year-old girl was walking to her Pennsylvania home from a Girl Scout Halloween Party. But during her walk home, a man witnessed her abduction. The town scoured for years to find out who killed this poor girl, and little did they know- the answer was right in front of them. This is the murder of Shauna Howe.
